name: Frida Punk 091 - FRIxDIEGO
description:
Frida Kahlo X Diego Rivera - 
An Artist in love with another Artist.
So much in love they married twice. There was much Frida had to say about her love of Diego.

“The most interesting thing about the so-called lies of Diego is that, sooner or later, the ones involved in the imaginary tale get angry, not because of the lies, but because of the truth contained in the lies, which always comes forth.” - Frida Kahlo

💎 LIMITED EDITION PUNK CELEBRATING THE UNION, LOVE, LUST, ART AND LIFE OF FRIDA KAHLO & DIEGO RIVERA.
